biography: Senior Data Scientist in Wolt's Personalization Team working on Carousel Ranking and Personalized Recommendations. Show Host of Recsperts - Recommender Systems Experts, the Podcast Show with industry and academia experts in Recommender Systems. Building Recommenders and Personalization Solutions with Python for various industries since 7+ years as well as creator and instructor of Python RecSys Training.
